Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.60,0:00:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色不错\N不错  不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.86,0:00:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦？看你脸色不太好耶\N主演白木优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.93,0:00:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N是吗   那我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.06,0:00:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导演   豆泽豆太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.86,0:00:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大岩露天温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.66,0:00:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里   大家是这里哟\N真不错呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.60,0:00:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错呀   露天温泉\N不错呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里哟   我们快点走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.93,0:01:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有遵守约定吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.93,0:01:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那给我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.20,0:02:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么? 快点脱啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.80,0:03:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪同老公一起参加了\N社区内旅游泡温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.93,0:04:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问我怎么会在同个社区的\N中野君面前摆出这个样子的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子小姐\N你那是什么眼神呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.06,0:05:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在社区举办的祭典酒会之后\N喝醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.73,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被同一社区内像弟弟般存在的\N中野君给强奸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.00,0:05:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯命是从的露出旅游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.06,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中野君拍下了被强奸中的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我进行了威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种态度没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.73,0:07:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给称老公看也没关系吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我很困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只有顺从我的话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子   你在干什么呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很不错哟\N是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.20,0:08:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位附近好像有个很大的湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.73,0:08:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大湖吗?  是的   稍后大家\N要一起去吗？好呀   想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.00,0:08:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去吧\N看湖不错呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位看这样的提议如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.26,0:09:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位先回房间个小时之 伪\N在旅店门前集合如何？   可以呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.40,0:09:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子不是一小时后\N是30分钟后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真守约定呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能适可而止呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.93,0:10:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行   社区内\N有名的全能美人太大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.73,0:10:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却对我唯命是从
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.73,0:10:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样有优越感的事\N一辈子都很难碰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.60,0:11:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之   在社区的旅游期间\N你必须听我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底应该怎么做呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.46,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了避免造成火灾\N把这个给灭掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用你的尿将它熄灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情怎么可能会做出来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.53,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经说过    如果不听我的话\N我就将心件事曝光出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.80,0:12:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿着内裤   尿不到的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把腿打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把它熄灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子   你像小狗一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到一个好点子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.00,0:14:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子   你就是小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.60,0:14:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子   我给你粮食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,含进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想被曝光吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一点也没有爽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我认真点做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.13,0:15:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我吞进去   深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.66,0:16:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不行了吗?\N让你更深一点    更深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你不要这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.86,0:16:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？\N会有人看至的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.33,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子   你在说什么了不起的话呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.40,0:17:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么不想被看到的话\N我让大家着看更加羞耻的吧   不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手抬起来\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.40,0:17:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,含进去\N露出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.13,0:17:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.33,0:18:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了\N这样的事情停止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行\N把嘴巴张开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N更加深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看向这边来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.06,0:18:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这边\N这边啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.93,0:18:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出\N把舌头伸出来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.00,0:18:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我舔阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吞到里面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.93,0:19:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想被曝光出来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.86,0:20:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来\N吸进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.93,0:20:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错    要吸进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我吸出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,含进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.86,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点吸进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.13,0:21:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.40,0:21:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难受吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.40,0:22:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难受是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.06,0:22:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.53,0:22:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.93,0:22:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你舔肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.46,0:22:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.93,0:23:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的舌头\N让我爽起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.20,0:24:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.00,0:24:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.73,0:24:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.93,0:24:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加快点速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.93,0:25:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.60,0:25:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要射了\N好好用你的舌头接着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.06,0:25:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.26,0:25:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.73,0:25:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了\N把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.80,0:25:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我弄干净一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.00,0:26:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.00,0:26:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子   大家要过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:24.86,0:26:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点穿好衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.86,0:26:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后过来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.33,0:27:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里了呢    真搞不懂呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.60,0:27:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起我来晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.13,0:27:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?优子她哪去啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.26,0:27:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.33,0:27:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.73,0:28:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.40,0:28:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子你去哪里啦?\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.20,0:28:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在附近转了一下\N真的吗？  那大好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.33,0:28:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们出发吧\N出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.93,0:29:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(好高兴呀)\N不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.60,0:29:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要这样\N要被大家看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:18.20,0:29:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(这样挺辛苦的吧)\N(是呀是呀)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.40,0:29:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（还有那么多呢）\N(已经快不行了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.26,0:29:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出声(是呀   我也这样觉得)\N不要这样   不要I(对吧   没错吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.80,0:29:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(差不多了   是吧)\N(差不多了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:41.26,0:29:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不行了\N(这么早就睡觉了吗？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:46.86,0:29:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(你平常都这样吗?)\N(差不多的吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.93,0:29:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(已经喝得差不多了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:58.33,0:30:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（还有这么多哟）\N（开玩笑的吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.20,0:30:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（帮大忙了）\N（这样就付了吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.53,0:30:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（别喝了）\N（再一起喝嘛）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:17.93,0:30:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老公已经醉烂如泥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.80,0:30:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.40,0:30:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(我们走吧)\N(去哪里呀)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:29.00,0:30:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子你是不是也在享受吁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.26,0:30:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.46,0:30:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(快点喝   继续喝)\N(喝吧喝吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:41.66,0:30:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(追加的菜怎么还不过来呀)\N(快点喝啦)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.73,0:30:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（喝呀你根本没有喝多少）\N（快点喝）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.80,0:30:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(我喝了很多了)\N(才没有呢)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:53.80,0:30:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(继续喝   喝吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:58.60,0:31:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(你真不能喝吗?)\N(你没事吧?)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.60,0:31:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来   继续喝)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:05.93,0:31:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(是真的不行啦)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.53,0:31:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(已经差不多啦)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.53,0:31:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(你作为老公应核也挺辛苦的吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.66,0:31:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(再来喝吧   继续喝)\N(没事的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:32.86,0:31:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(我真的不行了)\N(没事的   没意义呀这样)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.20,0:31:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呀?\N不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.66,0:31:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(我们继续喝吧   喝吧)\N(你喝醉 了吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.40,0:31:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(我没有醉)\N(那就继续喝吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.73,0:32:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(我不行了)\N(真弱呀)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.00,0:32:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(不是吧)\N(快点继续)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:24.86,0:32:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(追加的菜上来了哟)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.53,0:32:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(这里的菜挺好吃的)\N(味道不错)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:33.13,0:32:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:42.73,0:32:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(我觉得挺不错)\N(很好  很好)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:47.53,0:32:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(真开心呀)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.73,0:32:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(今天吃了好多呀)\N(还没结束哟)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.46,0:33:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍后我们再来玩更好玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:45.53,0:33:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们喝了不少呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.60,0:33:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他已经醉了\N没有了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.53,0:33:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他平时受有喝这么多的吧？\N喝不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.13,0:34:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N你跟你老公的感情真好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:04.20,0:34:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是把他送回房间比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.13,0:34:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧了\N送回房间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.40,0:34:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去送他回去吧\N我也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:17.26,0:34:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托了\N来吧  对不起呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:19.53,0:34:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N没事了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:29.66,0:34:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是喝大多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.26,0:34:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起呀\N没事啦   很可爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:37.93,0:34:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是给各位添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:43.13,0:34:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子你等一下要去逛小店吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:47.66,0:34:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逛小店？听说那家美容店效果很好\N真的吗?我们一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.46,0:35:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不去了\N我还得照顾我丈夫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:07.53,0:35:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起    请两位先过去吧\N那我们就先过去了好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:25.66,0:35:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以说不进温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:31.66,0:35:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又是什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.06,0:35:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂   干嘛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.06,0:35:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我办不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.86,0:35:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能做出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.53,0:35:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  你你就当是不小心进错了温泉\N然后诱惑男性就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.80,0:36:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:05.40,0:36:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到\N你想被曝光吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:35.66,0:37:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:43.53,0:37:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.40,0:38:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?这里为什么会有女人在?\N这里可能就是混浴    进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:23.53,0:38:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.53,0:39:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个\N怎么啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.33,0:39:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让 我舔你们的肉棒吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:27.80,0:39:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.33,0:39:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是   感觉还不错耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:37.00,0:39:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗？\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:41.40,0:39:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就恭敬不如从命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:44.60,0:39:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺不错的耶\N很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.93,0:39:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.93,0:40:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点开始呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:07.26,0:40:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚是你自己问能不能舔肉棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.13,0:40:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快点开始呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.26,0:40:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇   是来真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.26,0:40:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的手借给我用一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:41.26,0:40:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:54.20,0:40:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀\N那边也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:57.66,0:40:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.00,0:41:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会进男性温泉？\N然后渴望着肉棒呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:21.93,0:41:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为\N算了算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.73,0:41:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.86,0:41:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起来爽快吧\N对呀   对呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:30.20,0:41:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.73,0:41:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这边也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.06,0:41:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我揉一下这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.33,0:41:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的乳头硬起来了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:42.33,0:41:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 ？那我也来摸摸看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:47.26,0:41:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇   手感真好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.93,0:41:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两根一起舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:16.73,0:42:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了\N好爽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.73,0:42:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:48.73,0:42:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀\N吞得好深呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.66,0:43:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的事情太爽了\N让我来摸一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:28.60,0:43:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:41.26,0:43:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.20,0:43:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀\N乳头已经这么硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.06,0:44:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:14.60,0:44:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己先说想舔肉棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:18.86,0:44:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.86,0:44:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来拿着腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.66,0:44:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也很享受的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:18.06,0:45:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好下流的声音呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:25.00,0:45:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换你来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:31.53,0:45:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:04.06,0:46:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:25.00,0:46:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:29.40,0:46:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了   好舒服阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:40.33,0:46:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:56.06,0:46:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.40,0:47:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经这么湿了\N就那么爽吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:16.60,0:47:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来让我也爽一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:28.20,0:47:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:41.80,0:47:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:48.60,0:47:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:53.66,0:47:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了\N把腰给动起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:14.73,0:48:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:17.26,0:48:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到你的屁眼哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:33.93,0:48:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:03.26,0:49:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:06.73,0:49:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:10.86,0:49:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你弄得挺好的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:29.13,0:49:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能插入呢\N你想我插入的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:37.13,0:49:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以插入吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:42.86,0:49:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去吧  慢慢来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:02.86,0:50:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:25.80,0:50:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.26,0:51:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:12.73,0:51:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:15.26,0:51:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:17.40,0:51:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的身体哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:20.86,0:51:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:42.33,0:51:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:59.66,0:52:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.33,0:52:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀\N换我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:18.73,0:52:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝这边呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:26.60,0:52:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:32.33,0:52:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点舔呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:41.53,0:52:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽的呀\N真是淫荡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:07.93,0:53:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大厉害了\N换这边来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:13.00,0:53:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配合一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:43.13,0:53:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:22.33,0:54:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扶好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:46.20,0:55:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:03.66,0:56:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:09.40,0:56:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:16.06,0:56:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:18.73,0:56:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边来   趴在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:32.60,0:56:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我舔这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:35.13,0:56:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:07.26,0:57:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:35.66,0:57:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:47.26,0:57:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去了   要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:55.00,0:57:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以射出来吗？\N可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:19.13,0:58:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了\N要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:42.20,0:58:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮他舔干净   快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:59.00,0:58:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:10.33,0:59:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先休息一下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:55.66,0:59:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.60,1:00:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了\N帮我弄干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:48.33,1:00:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.33,1:01:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.86,1:01:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？\N爽吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:05.66,1:01:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会爽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:09.00,1:01:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个骗子\N明明这么有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:01.40,1:02:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了守护与老公的幸福生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.40,1:02:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能对中野君唯命是从
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:10.86,1:02:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心灵和肉体都已经达到了极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:19.80,1:02:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:28.86,1:02:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别出声
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:37.66,1:02:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:40.86,1:02:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经喝醉了   不会醒来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:45.13,1:02:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:45.00,1:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:54.46,1:04:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:05.40,1:05:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在优子你求饶之前\N我才会停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:14.86,1:05:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想我摸的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:22.33,1:05:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么进来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:41.26,1:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里挺敏感的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:46.60,1:05:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是想我摸的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:53.93,1:06:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这样的事\N你在逞强吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:10.46,1:06:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要醒来了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:23.53,1:06:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是喜欢这种事情的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:35.66,1:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺敏感的身体嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:46.20,1:06:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看   有感觉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:51.53,1:06:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你被摸了这么有感觉\N不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:28.73,1:07:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样被模\N)让你很兴奋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:45.66,1:07:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很想被我摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:21.00,1:08:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连声音都控制不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:41.13,1:08:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老公在旁边睡着\N让你更加兴奋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:48.33,1:08:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:53.00,1:08:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎\N看你的乳头这么硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:02.20,1:09:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有感觉\N优子你是骗子
